2. **Ex Parte Hearing Information.** I intend to appear **ex parte** in **Department R12** on **[Ex Parte Date]** at **[Time]** to request an **Order Shortening Time** on Plaintiff’s pending **Motion to Compel Defendant’s Deposition; Request for Monetary Sanctions; and Request for Limited Leave After Cutoff** and to set a condensed briefing schedule. I will not seek a merits ruling ex parte.

