   Fax (if any): **[Fax]**

4. **Manner of Notice.** I gave notice by **[email/telephone/voicemail/text/fax/personal delivery]**.

   * If by email: I sent an email to **[email address]** at **[time]** with the subject line **“Ex Parte—OST on Motion to Compel (Romero v. Bentley, CIVRS2501874)”**.
